Sub Main
' This macro pastes the contents of the clipboard as unformatted text and
' merges the topics if the content is broken down into multiple topics
' as a result of the paste opertion in MM.

ActiveDocument.Selection.PasteSpecial(mmPasteSpecialPriorityUnformattedText)

MacroRun (MacroDir & "\MergeTopics.mmbas")

End Sub
